<p>This fundraiser will have a little twist to it though. Because of my inclination towards all things Internet I have opened up the 50/50 draw as well as a draw for a <a href="http://www.theflip.com/products_flip_ultra.shtml">Flip Ultra video camera</a> to the online community. Each Canadian dollar contributed to the draws will enter your name into the draw once. If there is enough interest online I am thinking of adding more prizes as well, so let me know what you think.</p>
