<p>Lately I have learned a lot about the integratabilty (I think that&#8217;s a word) and flexibility of Wordpress and it&#8217;s ability to work with other online applications and tools.</p>
<p>For example: my portfolio is piggy-backing on <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/jmeallen/">my Flickr account</a> using <a href="http://tantannoodles.com/toolkit/photo-album/" target="_blank">this Wordpress plugin</a> and my &#8216;life stream&#8217; (aka record of online activities aka you can stalk me here) has been integrated and customized from this <a href="http://friendfeed.com/embed/widget" target="_blank">Friendfeed widget embed code</a>.</p>
<p>There are still a few wrinkles to iron out and some portfolio chunks missing, but take a look around and please let me know what you think!</p>
<p>The photo is just for fun. From a trip up north with some friends.</p>
