<p>The cover for the book <strong><em>rabble.ca [best of 2008]</em></strong>. Edited by Jenn Watt.</p>
<p>I was asked to make a design for the annual Best of rabble.ca collection. It was a collection of articles from the 2008 year. Something simple and grabbing.</p>
<p>There were five sections to the book: interviews; reporting; analysis; commentary and arts &amp; books.  I created an icon to represent each section and adopted the colour scheme from the website.</p>
<img src="http://feeds2.feedburner.com/~r/eimaj/~4/YG7L1JBMk1I" height="1" width="1"/>";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:44:"http://eimaj.net/rabbleca-best-of-2008/feed/";}s:10:"feedburner";a:1:{s:8:"origlink";s:39:"http://eimaj.net/rabbleca-best-of-2008/";}s:7:"summary";s:95:"The cover for the book <em><strong>rabble.ca [best of 2008]</strong></em>. Edited by Jenn Watt.";s:12:"atom_content";s:824:"<p><a class="tt-flickr tt-flickr-Medium" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/jmeallen/3307576593/"><img class="alignleft" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3468/3307576593_dc1a54e39b.jpg" border="0" alt="rabble.ca [best of 2008]" width="357" height="500" /></a></p>
<p>The cover for the book <strong><em>rabble.ca [best of 2008]</em></strong>. Edited by Jenn Watt.</p>
<p>I was asked to make a design for the annual Best of rabble.ca collection. It was a collection of articles from the 2008 year. Something simple and grabbing.</p>
<p>There were five sections to the book: interviews; reporting; analysis; commentary and arts &amp; books.  I created an icon to represent each section and adopted the colour scheme from the website.</p>
